OL,3,CWest of England Mayor says activists
OL,4,Cmade her feel 'trapped and unsafe'
OL,6,FThe Mayor of the West of England has
OL,7,Fsaid she was left feeling "trapped and
OL,8,Funsafe" after allegedly being followed
OL,9,Finto a lift by a campaigner.
OL,11,FLabour's Helen Godwin, who was elected
OL,12,Fin 2025, claims she was chased by a
OL,13,Fgroup of shouting protesters when
OL,14,Fleaving a committee meeting in Bristol
OL,15,Fon Monday, 23 March.
OL,17,FIn a statement posted to the West of
OL,18,FEngland Combined Authority website,
OL,19,Fshe said she was then followed into a
OL,20,Flift by a man who refused to leave.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
