PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774530670
OL,3,CWest of England Mayor says activists
OL,4,Cmade her feel 'trapped and unsafe'
OL,6,F"Aggression is not activism, and
OL,7,Ftactics like this designed to
OL,8,Fintimidate politicians have no place
OL,9,Fin our society," Ms Godwin said.
OL,11,FMs Godwin said she prides herself on
OL,12,F"talking to people across the West
OL,13,FCountry every day," describing it as
OL,14,Fan "important part of our democracy".
OL,16,F"But today, as I tried to leave the
OL,17,Froom, a group of people ran after me -
OL,18,Fshouting," she continued.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774530670
OL,3,CWest of England Mayor says activists
OL,4,Cmade her feel 'trapped and unsafe'
OL,6,F"A man followed me into a lift and
OL,7,Frefused to leave, despite being asked
OL,8,Frepeatedly.
OL,10,F"People, particularly women, will
OL,11,Funderstand just how scary this was. I
OL,12,Ffelt trapped and unsafe. The police
OL,13,Fhad to be called, and they are now
OL,14,Finvestigating.
OL,16,FACORN confirmed their members "met
OL,17,F(Godwin) in the corridor outside and
OL,18,Ftried to ask questions", but denied
OL,19,Ftrapping her.
OL,26,@yD@ApmyD@Hpn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
