PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774530670
OL,3,CWest of England Mayor says activists
OL,4,Cmade her feel 'trapped and unsafe'
OL,6,FThey said the mayor was unwilling to
OL,7,Fengage with their questions in the
OL,8,FOverview and Scrutiny committee
OL,9,Fmeeting.
OL,11,F"It's very disappointing to see the
OL,12,Fmayor completely blow questions being
OL,13,Fasked out of proportion, to avoid
OL,14,Ftaking responsibility for promises she
OL,15,Fmade," they said.
OL,17,FA spokesman for Avon and Somerset
OL,18,FPolice said officers attended the West
OL,19,Fof England Combined Authority offices
OL,20,Fon Redcliff Street at about 10:30 am
OL,21,Fon Monday 23 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
