OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1774530670
OL,3,CWest of England Mayor says activists
OL,4,Cmade her feel 'trapped and unsafe'
OL,6,F"We received a report that an elected
OL,7,Fofficial was confronted by members of
OL,8,Fthe public following a meeting," the
OL,9,Fspokesman said.
OL,11,FThe force said enquiries into the
OL,12,Fincident are ongoing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
